## Overview

The Help Assistant is a built-in AI chat panel available from every page in Graphium AI. It answers questions about the Graphium AI platform in real time, drawing its responses from published documentation and providing source links so you can read the full article if you need more detail.

The Help Assistant is available to all authenticated users — no vault access is required.

---

## Opening and Closing the Help Panel

### Opening the panel

Click the **? (help) icon** in the global header at the top right of the screen. The Help panel slides out from the right side of the page.

The panel stays open as you navigate around Graphium — you can keep it open while working in a vault, switching pages, or using other features without losing your conversation.

