**Keyboard shortcut:** Press **`⌘ Shift H`** on Mac or **`Ctrl Shift H`** on Windows/Linux to toggle the panel open or closed from anywhere in the dashboard.

---

### Closing the panel

Close the Help panel using any of these methods:

- Click the **✕** button in the top-right corner of the panel.
- Click the **? (help) icon** in the header again to toggle it closed.
- Press **`Esc`** when the panel is focused.

Closing the panel does not end your conversation — when you reopen it during the same session, your previous messages are still there.

