## Continuing a Conversation

You can ask follow-up questions in the same conversation — the assistant maintains context from previous messages within your active session.

Your conversation persists as long as the Graphium dashboard tab remains open. If you close or refresh the page, log out, or switch to a different workspace or account, the conversation is cleared and the panel returns to its empty state the next time you open it.

> 💡 **Tip:** If you want to start fresh without navigating away, click **+ New conversation** in the top-right corner of the panel. This clears the current thread immediately.

